<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.sonm.monfree</id>

  <name>MonFree</name>
  <summary>MonFree – Audio Sequencer</summary>

  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>LicenseRef-proprietary</project_license>

  <developer_name>sonm</developer_name>

  <description>
    <p>MonFree is a sample-based audio sequencer.</p>
    <p>This is the official Flatpak release, maintained directly by the upstream developer.</p>
    <p>Core Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>32-pad grid with hands-on keyboard control</li>
      <li>Step sequencer with 16 steps per pattern and 32 patterns per project</li>
      <li>Real-time effects including EQ, Compressor, and Saturator</li>
      <li>Built-in resampling and WAV export</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Sequencer:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>32 Pads</li>
      <li>16 Steps per Pattern</li>
      <li>32 Patterns</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Samples:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>32 Samples</li>
      <li>Max 10 seconds per Sample</li>
      <li>WAV format</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Effects / Options:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pattern and Song Effects: Gain, BPM, High Pass, Low Pass, EQ Pre, Compressor, Saturator, EQ Post</li>
      <li>Pad and Step Effects: Gain, Pitch, High Pass, Low Pass, EQ Pre, Compressor, Saturator, EQ Post</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Presets:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>LoFi, EDM, Hardstyle, Phonk, Trap</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Resampling:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Mono Mix, Reverse, 8 bit 10 kHz</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Export:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>WAV</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Controls and Shortcuts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Play/Stop: Spacebar</li>
      <li>For fast, hands-on pad control, use your computer keyboard: 1 2 3 4 | q w e r | a s d f | z x c v</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

